《'''裸體、綠葉和半身像'''》（{{lang-fr|''Nu au Plateau de Sculpteur''}}）是[[巴勃羅·畢卡索|巴勃羅·畢卡索]]於1932年所畫的一幅油畫，主題是其情婦[[瑪麗-德雷莎·華特|瑪麗-德雷莎·華特]]（Marie-Thérèse Walter）。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601088&sid=aRQu28TfO1dM|title=Picasso Nude Sells for Record $106.5 Million at Christie's N.Y.|work=Bloomberg|accessdate=5 May 2010|archive-date=2010-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100506032701/http://www.bloomberg.com/apps/news?pid=20601088&sid=aRQu28TfO1dM|dead-url=no}}</ref>此幅油畫是由[[洛杉磯|洛杉磯]]的錫德尼·布羅迪（Sidney Brody）及弗朗西斯·布魯迪（Frances Brody）夫婦自1950年代起一直收藏，自他們收藏這幅畫作後，僅於1961年作其唯一一次的公開展覽。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/arts_and_culture/8661338.stm|title=Picasso painting fetches record $106m at auction|work=BBC|accessdate=5 May 2010|archive-date=2010-05-07|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507123707/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/entertainment/arts_and_culture/8661338.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref>  

==拍賣==
2010年5月4日，此幅畫作於[[紐約|紐約]][[佳士得|佳士得]]出售。這幅畫是洛杉磯慈善家弗朗西斯的其中一幅收藏作品，弗朗西斯於2009年11月去世。在與以倫敦為總部的[[蘇富比|蘇富比]]競爭中，佳士得獲得這批收藏的拍賣權。全部收藏價值估計超過150,000,000美元，而原本預期《裸體、綠葉和半身像》在拍賣中可為卖家賺取80,000,000美元。<ref name=nyt>{{cite web |url=http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/10/arts/design/10auction.html |title=Christie's Wins Bid to Auction $150 Million Brody Collection |work=New York Times |accessdate=5 May 2010 |archive-date=2010-03-15 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100315181206/http://www.nytimes.com/2010/03/10/arts/design/10auction.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

超過六個人出價競投，而成功投得此畫的買家透過電話出價95,000,000美元。連同[[買家佣金|買家佣金]]（buyer's premium），此畫的售價達到106,500,000美元。<ref name="BBC News">{{cite news|url=http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8497287.stm|title=Giacometti sculpture fetches £65m at Sotheby's auction|work=BBC|accessdate=3 February 2010|archive-date=2019-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191211123912/http://news.bbc.co.uk/1/hi/uk/8497287.stm|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.today.msnbc.msn.com/id/36950780/ns/today-entertainment/ |title=Picasso painting sells for record $106.5 million |work=New York Times |accessdate=5 May 2010 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100507012157/http://today.msnbc.msn.com/id/36950780/ns/today-entertainment/ |archivedate=2010年5月7日 |df= }}</ref>不計[[通脹|通脹]]，《裸體、綠葉和半身像》打破了[[賈克梅蒂|賈克梅蒂]]的《[[行走的人I|行走的人I]]》（''L'Homme qui marche I''）於2010年2月拍賣的紀錄，該作品的成交價為104,300,000美元。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/04/picasso-sold-at-auction-for-106-5-million-a-world-record/?src=mv|title=Picasso Sells at Auction for $106.5 Million, a Record for a Work of Art|work=New York Times|accessdate=5 May 2010|archive-date=2010-07-09|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20100709191412/http://artsbeat.blogs.nytimes.com/2010/05/04/picasso-sold-at-auction-for-106-5-million-a-world-record/?src=mv|dead-url=no}}</ref> 現在仍然是[[最昂贵画作列表|世界最昂贵画作之一]]。

